The paper describes the use of a deep learning network to predict future blood glucose levels, which involves time series analysis and sequential modeling. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves medical applications, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
